# Kernel-materialised secrets — these live in the CC `secrets` table and are written into
# Library/processes/secrets/ at runtime by pete-session-bootstrap.py / railway-bootstrap.py.
# They must NEVER be committed. The whole Library/ tree is runtime-materialised
# (secrets + helper symlinks) — the repo tracks no Library/ content, so ignore it all.
Library/

# Python bytecode
__pycache__/
*.pyc

# Local caches / scratch
*.cache.md
